result.title: 125 Div 2 added
result.content:
I have added a contest (125 Div2) to the group contest page. You can try it out and then we can discuss if any one feels difficulty. The solutions and editorials of this contest are already available. So, please try to do Virtual Participation and don't read solutions or editorials before trying them on your own.

Please post your query if you have doubts in comments in this post. And check this group regularly for updates.
